Assignment 4
SPIN model checking
=============================

Requirements:
You need executable spin file IN CURRENT FOLDER. If you get error message like:
	make: ./spin: Command not found

Then you have to do one of these two options.
  1) Compile SPIN: put source code into ./src/ folder, and use `make spinmake`.
  2) If you already install SPIN in system, then just type:
	$) cp $(which spin) ./


Usage:
  1) Compile:
	$) make
  2) Run:
	$) make run
  3) Trace (if it has bug):
	$) make trace
